<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Malgun Gothic, 맑은 고딕, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; margin-block-end: unset; white-space: pre-line; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="modal-inner__title font-noto" style="box-sizing: border-box; word-break: keep-all; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 28px; line-height: 41px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;; display: block; text-align: center; white-space: normal;">이용약관</span><div class="modal-inner__desc scroll" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow-y: auto; max-height: 42vh; margin-top: 9px; line-height: 1.5; border-radius: 5px; padding: 0px 10px 10px; font-size: 14px;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 10px;">제1장 총칙</p>
